   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify;margin-right:0.0694in;text-indent:0.3937in"><span xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">warden, housemother, matron, nurse, head nurse, senior nursing officer, tutor, </span><span style="font-weight:bold" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">protector</span></p>
