   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">1 Compatible to some degree 2 Not a seamless integration </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">"You can </span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">use it in conjunction with</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US"> our product" </span></p>
