   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">1 Benefit 2 Help </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">"Where is the </span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">value add</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US"> in having purchasing's opinion?" </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">Vesting period</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">1 The number of years before an employee owns his employer paid benefit 2 The percent owned by the employee that grows over the entire period. This increase is rarely steady and can be from 0 to 10 years or more </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">"The 401k has a 7 year </span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">vesting period</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">" </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">Viable</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">1 Able to last for a least a while </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">"It is still </span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">viable</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US"> " </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">W</span></p>
