   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">1 Ask you to believe 2 A desire to be believed with little evidence offered </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">"I </span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">want you to feel</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US"> this" </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">Weak market</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">1 Price is falling due to a low demand </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">"We can not sell more because of the </span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">weak market</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">" </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">See: </span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="ru-RU" lang="ru-RU">Strong market</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">Well behaved price</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">1 Stable price 2 A price that is little changed 3 A price which is not falling or rising over time </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">"We can predict our costs because of the </span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">well behaved prices</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">" </span></p>
