   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">1 A broader point of view 2 Looking at other related topics. </span></p>
   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">"It is not so important in a </span><span style="font-style:italic;font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">wider context</span><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">" </span></p>
