   <p dir="ltr" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;color:#000000" xml:lang="en-US" lang="en-US">1 Do all that is necessary to obtain the desired result 2 Do what little may be needed to be done 3 Do nothing to prevent the desired result </span></p>
